---
title: Pan-Seared Striploin and Savoury Mushroom  Gravy with Asparagus and Wild Rice
description: Asparagus season isn't long in Canada, so we must make the most of it! Miso and mushrooms are a perfect pairing for an umami-rich sauce in this unbelievable steak dinner.
